'''Yamada Shrine''' (山田神社) refers to various {{ill|Shinto shrines|ja|神社|12=draft|12=draft}} located across Japan.
* '''Kanagawa Prefecture''' ** {{ill|Yamada Shrine (Yokohama City)|ja|山田神社 (横浜市)|12=draft|12=draft}} - Located in Minamiyamada Town, {{ill|Tsuzuki Ward|ja|都筑区|12=draft|12=draft}}, Yokohama City. A shrine designated for offerings and former village shrine.
* '''Osaka Prefecture''' ** {{ill|Yamada Shrine (Hirakata City Yamanoue)|ja|山田神社 (枚方市山之上)|12=draft|12=draft}} - Located in Yamanoue, {{ill|Hirakata City|ja|枚方市|12=draft|12=draft}}. A former village shrine. ** {{ill|Yamada Shrine (Hirakata City Taguchi)|ja|山田神社 (枚方市田口)|12=draft|12=draft}} - Located in Taguchi, Hirakata City. A former village shrine.
* '''Yamaguchi Prefecture''' ** {{ill|Yamada Shrine (Yamaguchi City)|ja|山田神社 (山口市)|12=draft|12=draft}} - Located in Ato Jifuku Kami, {{ill|Yamaguchi City|ja|山口市|12=draft|12=draft}}. ** '''Yamada Shrine (Suō Province)''' - A shrine listed in the historical records of Suō Province. *** {{ill|Yamada Shrine (Suō-Ōshima Town)|ja|山田神社 (周防大島町)|12=draft|12=draft}} - Located in Sotoiri, Suō-Ōshima Town, Ōshima District, Yamaguchi Prefecture. A candidate for the above shrine. *** {{ill|Yamada Shrine (Shikano Town)|ja|山田神社 (鹿野町)|12=draft|12=draft}} - Previously located in Shikano Town, now part of Shunan City, Yamaguchi Prefecture. Referred to as {{ill|Nisho Yamada Shrine|ja|二所山田神社|12=draft|12=draft}}.
* '''Kagawa Prefecture''' ** {{ill|Yamada Shrine (Kanonji City)|ja|山田神社 (観音寺市)|12=draft|12=draft}} - Located in Kuda Town, {{ill|Kanonji City|ja|観音寺市|12=draft|12=draft}}. A former village shrine and a {{ill|Shikinai shrine|ja|式内社|1=Shikinaisha|12=draft|12=draft}}. {{citation needed|Yamada Shrine}}
[[simple:user:immanuelle/山田神社]]
